  "body": "Output of `helm version`:\r\n\r\nv3.0.0-alpha.1\r\n\r\nHelm errors when the chart contains a resource in a different namespace than the current kube-context, even when the user has cluster-admin access. \r\n\r\n```\r\nthe namespace from the provided object \\\"target\\\" does not match the namespace \\\"default\\\". You must pass '--namespace=target' to perform this operation.\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis prevents charts with resources in multiple namespaces from being installed.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
